                            RFC

    RFC documents contain technical specifications and organizational notes for the Internet.


IETF : (The Internet Engineering Task Force)
    . "the overall goal of the IETF is to make the Internet work better."
    . its mission is to produce high quality, and engineering documents that influence 
    the way people design, use, and manage the Internet in such a way as to make the Internet work better.


poll() : (Polling the network)
    Poll the network to retrieve information from network devices that you can use to monitor the behavior of the devices.

